  "data": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p><strong>Prerequisites:</strong> Dark sphere (Hide In Darkness (meld)), caster level 5th</p>\n<p>When you apply the Hide In Darkness meld to a target, its benefits function in any area of dim light or darkness, not just areas of darkness you created.</p>\n<p>In addition, when you apply the meld to a target you may spend an additional point to completely hide them from detection. Anyone that attempts to discern the target&#8217;s location must succeed on the normal Perception check to locate them while they are hiding, even those using unusual forms of perception such as blindsight or tremorsense or Divination sphere effects to directly or indirectly discover their current position.</p>\n",
